\@writefile{lot}{\contentsline {table}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces Sample-level escalation accuracy under different interventions, evaluated against the optimal policy for cost ratio $R = 4$ ($\tau ^* = 80\%$, $c_w = 4 c_\ell $). For each sample, the correct action is to escalate if the condition's predictive accuracy is below 75\% and implement if above. MoralMachine is excluded from all rows. GPT-5-mini further excludes MovieLens due to content filter restrictions.}}{8}{table.caption.10}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{tab:interventions}{{1}{8}{Sample-level escalation accuracy under different interventions, evaluated against the optimal policy for cost ratio $R = 4$ ($\tau ^* = 80\%$, $c_w = 4 c_\ell $). For each sample, the correct action is to escalate if the condition's predictive accuracy is below 75\% and implement if above. MoralMachine is excluded from all rows. GPT-5-mini further excludes MovieLens due to content filter restrictions}{table.caption.10}{}}
